text: Eiffel 65 is an Italian Italodance/Eurodance music group. The group has three members in it. The members of the group are Jeffrey Jey, Gabry Ponte and Maurizio Lobina. They made an album called Europop. They are most famous for their songs "Blue (Da Ba Dee)" and "Move Your Body". == Discography == ===Albums=== *Europop (1999) *Contact!
